Remarks

This property affects NumberOfReps. This also determines how this property will be written to file.

ID

Hexadecimal identifier for this property. XMLExemplarProperty and AllProperties.

public override uint ID { get; set; }

Property Value

uint

NumberOfReps

The number of repetitions of DataType this property has. This informs (in part) how many bytes to read for this property. Initialized to 0.

public override int NumberOfReps { get; }

Property Value

int

Remarks

Determining the count partially depends on the encoding type. For binary encoded float-type properties: 0 reps = single value, 1 reps = multiple values but currently held to 1 value (problematic on macOS), n reps = n number of values. For text encoded float-type properties: n reps = n number of values.
